select /* TPC-DS query29.tpl 0.53 */   
     i_item_id
    ,i_item_desc
    ,s_store_id

   ,date_dim             d3
   ,store
   ,item

 and d2.d_moy               between 4 and  4 + 3

 and sr_customer_sk         = cs_bill_customer_sk
 and sr_item_sk             = cs_item_sk
 and cs_sold_date_sk        = d3.d_date_sk     
 and d3.d_year              in (1998,1998+1,1998+2)
 group by
    i_item_id
   ,i_item_desc
   ,s_store_id
   ,s_store_name
 order by
    i_item_id 
   ,i_item_desc
   ,s_store_id
   ,s_store_name
 limit 100
